The '''RX-series pilot droid''' was a line of [[pilot]] [[droid]]s produced by [[Industrial Automaton]].<ref name="Star Wars Rebels: Head to Head" />

{{Droid-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The RX-series pilot droid originally appeared in [[Star Tours (real-world)|''Star Tours'']], a simulator ride that operated at Disney Parks worldwide from [[1987]] to [[2016]], and its successor/prequel, ''[[Star Tours: The Adventures Continue]]'', from [[2012]] to the present. In the original attraction, RX-series droid [[RX-24/Legends|RX-24]] (aka "Rex") serves as the pilot for riders' [[StarSpeeder 3000]] [[Star Tours Flight 45|flight]] to [[Endor/Legends|Endor]].

